 1997-12481997-08-280,  ,  ,  ,  HERITAGE
PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1995-496 of March 27, 1995 which appointed P. ANDRÉE WYLIE as full-time member of the Canadian Radio- television and Telecommunications Commission, by deleting the words "for a term of three years" and substituting the words "for a term of five years".

Amendment to Order in Council P.C. 1995-496 of March 27, 1995 which
appointed P. ANDRÉE WYLIE as full-time member of the Canadian Radio-
